These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-1::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: writing, rock-climbing, singing
There 3 different types of food: orange, peas, spinach
The people have 3 different jobs:  doctor, entrepreneur, paramedic
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, jet-ski, tram
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, poppy, azalea
There are 3 different nationalities: german, russian, spanish
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, climbing
 1. the person driving the tram is the paramedic##1
 2. the paramedic is on the right of the spanish##1
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is the entrepreneur##1
 4. the german is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is the person driving the jet-ski##1
 6. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 7. the paramedic is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 8. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 9. the person eating peas is the person who's hobby is singing##1
10. the person eating orange is on the right of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby      | writing  | rock-climbing   | singing      |
| Food          | spinach      | orange     | peas     |
| Job           | entrepreneur | paramedic  | doctor   |
| Transport   | jet-ski   | tram     | trike  |
| Flower   | daffodil      | poppy      | azalea      |
| Nationality   | spanish      | russian    | german   |
| Sport         | badminton    | basketball | climbing |

