.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, photography, traveling
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, journalist, teacher
There are 3 different favourite colors: lilac, purple, azure
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, italian, nigerian
House: ranch-style, cape-cod, craftsman
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, march, april
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, tram, van
 1. the italian is in the middle##1
 2. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person who's birthday is in may##1
 3. the person driving the tram is in the middle##1
 4. the person who's hobby is photography is the craftsman house##1
 5. the chef is on the far left##1
 6. the nigerian is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
 9. the person driving the van is on the far left##1
10. the teacher is the ranch-style house##1
11. the journalist is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |
| Hobby         | photography | traveling  | hiking     |
| Job           | chef        | journalist | teacher    |
| Color   | purple  | azure    | lilac    |
| Nationality   | nigerian    | italian    | egyptian   |
| House           | craftsman        | cape-cod    | ranch-style        |
| Birthday         | march     | may  | april     |
| Transport     | van         | tram       | skateboard |

