 2. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left##1
 3. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
 4. the person who likes purple is on the right of the dutch##1
 5. the person eating broccoli is on the far right##1
 6. the person watching superhero movies is the person traveling to prague##1
 7. the dressmaker is on the right of the pakistani##1
 8. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person eating lime##1
 9. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the dressmaker##1
10. the freelancer is the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |
| City      | prague   | new-york         | paris |
| Food          | zucchini  | lime        | broccoli    |
