The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, zombie
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, january, november
There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, malaysian, nigerian
3 different pets are kept: snake, hamster, ferret
 1. the security-guard is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 2. the person watching animation movies is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 3. the palace house is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 4. the owner of the snake is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 6. the project-manager is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 7. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 8. the nigerian is in the middle##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the victorian house##1
10. the malaysian is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
11. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |        2        |       3        |
| House      | palace   | cottage        | victorian           |
| Hobby         | collecting | sudoku          | gardening      |
| Job           | engineer   | project-manager | security-guard |
| Movie-Genre   | animation  | adventure       | zombie         |
| Birthday   | january    | november          | august        |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | nigerian        | indonesian     |
| Pet         | snake   | ferret         | hamster       |

