.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-18::.
There are 3 different nationalities: american, pakistani, dutch
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, siglo, montecristo
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, reading, sudoku
The people have 3 different jobs:  doctor, musician, videographer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, disaster, time-travel
City: venice, san-francisco, miami
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, ship, van
 1. the person driving the ship is the person who's hobby is reading##1
 2. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person who's hobby is reading##1
 3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
 4. the old-henry-smoker is on the far right##1
 5. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the american##1
 7. the dutch is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 8. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 9. the doctor is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
10. the pakistani is the person watching time-travel movies##1
11. the doctor is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
12. the videographer is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |      3      |
| Nationality      | american       | dutch      | pakistani      |
| Cigar          | siglo        | montecristo | old-henry   |
| Hobby         | sudoku       | reading    | card-games  |
| Job           | videographer | doctor     | musician    |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy       | disaster   | time-travel |
| City         | miami        | san-francisco   | venice     |
| Transport     | van          | ship       | bus         |

