.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-19::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, motorbike, train
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, asparagus, cherry
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, mystery, superhero
There are 3 different favourite colors: aquamarine, amber, blood-red
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, egyptian, japanese
3 different pets are kept: bird, rabbit, turtle
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, rose, tulip
 1. the person who growsazalea is on the far right##1
 2. the person driving the train is in the middle##1
 3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
 4. the argentine is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
 5. the person who growstulip is on the far left##1
 6. the person eating asparagus is on the far left##1
 7. the japanese is the owner of the rabbit##1
 8. the japanese is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 9. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
10. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |      3      |
| Transport      | motorbike      | train         | snowmobile |
| Food          | asparagus | cherry        | artichoke   |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | mystery       | superhero   |
| Color   | aquamarine   | blood-red          | amber       |
| Nationality   | egyptian  | japanese      | argentine   |
| Pet           | turtle    | rabbit        | bird        |
| Flower         | tulip  | rose | azalea     |

