.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, tea
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, cain, davidoff
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, hiking, woodworking
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, february, september
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, hip-hop, salsa
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, malaysian, russian
There are 3 different favourite colors: black, yellow, brown
 1. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 2. the person drinking tea is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
 4. the cain-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 5. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the russian##1
 6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the australian##1
 7. the person who likes yellow is the australian##1
 8. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
 9. the fan of salsa is in the middle##1
10. the person who likes brown is in the middle##1
11. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |      3      |
| Beverage      | cola       | coffee     | tea         |
| Cigar          | cain      | siglo  | davidoff     |
| Hobby         | collecting | hiking     | woodworking |
| Birthday   | may  | september | february     |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep    | salsa      | hip-hop     |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | russian    | australian  |
| Color           | black   | brown      | yellow      |

 